statements: SELECT trade_id, trade_type, trade_timestamp, trade_symbol, trade_price, trade_volume FROM trade_execution_optimization;
SELECT trade_symbol, trade_timestamp, trade_volume, trade_id, trade_type, trade_price FROM trade_execution_optimization;
SELECT trade_timestamp, trade_volume, trade_symbol, trade_price, trade_id, trade_type FROM trade_execution_optimization;
SELECT trade_id, trade_timestamp, trade_type, trade_volume, trade_symbol, trade_price FROM trade_execution_optimization ORDER BY trade_timestamp DESC;
SELECT * FROM trade_execution_optimization WHERE trade_volume > 1000 ORDER BY trade_price DESC;
SELECT * FROM trade_execution_optimization WHERE trade_id = 100;
SELECT trade_symbol, trade_price, trade_timestamp FROM trade_execution_optimization WHERE trade_price > 1000;
SELECT trade_type, trade_symbol, trade_timestamp, trade_volume FROM trade_execution_optimization WHERE trade_type = 'BUY' ORDER BY trade_timestamp DESC;
SELECT trade_id, trade_symbol, trade_volume, trade_timestamp, trade_type FROM trade_execution_optimization WHERE trade_volume > 500 ORDER BY trade_timestamp ASC, trade_volume DESC;
SELECT trade_id, trade_symbol, trade_price, trade_timestamp FROM trade_execution_optimization WHERE trade_symbol = 'AAPL' AND trade_type = 'SELL' ORDER BY trade_price DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT * FROM Trades ORDER BY trade_date DESC, executed_price ASC;
SELECT symbol, trade_quantity FROM Trades WHERE trade_quantity > 100;
SELECT symbol, trade_quantity, trade_date FROM Trades WHERE trade_date BETWEEN '2022-06-01' AND '2022-06-30';
SELECT trade_id, symbol, executed_price FROM Trades WHERE executed_price >= 50.00 ORDER BY executed_price DESC;
SELECT order_id, symbol, order_quantity, order_type FROM Orders ORDER BY order_date ASC, order_quantity DESC;
SELECT trade_id, trade_date, symbol, trade_quantity, executed_price FROM Trades WHERE trade_date >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT symbol, trade_quantity FROM Trades WHERE trade_quantity > 1000 ORDER BY trade_quantity DESC;
SELECT order_id, order_date, symbol, order_quantity, order_type, order_status FROM Orders WHERE order_quantity BETWEEN 500 AND 1000;
SELECT trade_id, trade_date, symbol, trade_quantity, executed_price FROM Trades WHERE symbol LIKE '%AAPL%';
SELECT order_id, order_date, symbol, order_quantity, order_type, order_status FROM Orders ORDER BY order_date DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT * FROM trade_orders ORDER BY order_id DESC;
SELECT symbol, quantity, price FROM trade_orders WHERE executed = TRUE;
SELECT * FROM trade_executions WHERE execution_price > 100 ORDER BY executed_time ASC;
SELECT order_id, symbol, quantity, price FROM trade_orders WHERE quantity >= 100 AND price < 50;
SELECT execution_id, order_id, executed_time, execution_price FROM trade_executions ORDER BY execution_id ASC;
SELECT * FROM trade_orders;
SELECT symbol, quantity, price FROM trade_orders WHERE executed = FALSE;
SELECT order_id, symbol, quantity, price, executed FROM trade_orders WHERE quantity > 100 ORDER BY price DESC;
SELECT * FROM trade_executions JOIN trade_orders ON trade_executions.order_id = trade_orders.order_id;
SELECT th.* FROM trade_history th JOIN trade_executions te ON th.execution_id = te.execution_id WHERE te.execution_price > 50;
SELECT * FROM trades ORDER BY trade_timestamp DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT trade_symbol, trade_quantity, trade_price FROM trades WHERE trade_quantity > 100 ORDER BY trade_timestamp ASC;
SELECT trade_symbol, trade_price FROM trades WHERE trade_price > 500 ORDER BY trade_price DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT trade_symbol, trade_quantity FROM trades WHERE trade_symbol LIKE 'AAPL%' OR trade_quantity >= 500 ORDER BY trade_symbol ASC;
SELECT trade_symbol, trade_quantity, trade_price FROM trades WHERE trade_timestamp BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-02-01' ORDER BY trade_timestamp ASC LIMIT 20;
SELECT * FROM trades WHERE trade_quantity > 100 ORDER BY trade_price DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT trade_symbol, COUNT(*) FROM trades GROUP BY trade_symbol HAVING COUNT(*) > 5 ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC;
SELECT trader_name, trader_email FROM traders ORDER BY trader_name ASC, trader_email ASC LIMIT 5;
SELECT trade_symbol, AVG(trade_price) FROM trades GROUP BY trade_symbol HAVING AVG(trade_price) > 50 ORDER BY trade_symbol ASC;

SELECT orders.order_id, executions.execution_quantity, trades.trade_symbol FROM orders JOIN executions ON orders.order_id = executions.order_id JOIN trades ON orders.trade_id = trades.trade_id WHERE orders.side = 'BUY' AND executions.execution_quantity > 50 ORDER BY orders.order_id ASC, executions.execution_quantity DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT * FROM trades;
SELECT trade_id, symbol, trade_price FROM trades WHERE trade_volume > 100;
SELECT symbol, trade_volume FROM trades WHERE symbol = 'AAPL';
SELECT * FROM orders ORDER BY order_id DESC;
SELECT user_id, username, email FROM users WHERE username LIKE 'john%';
SELECT * FROM trades ORDER BY trade_id DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT symbol, trade_volume FROM trades WHERE trade_price > 100 ORDER BY trade_volume ASC;
SELECT username, first_name, last_name, email FROM users WHERE username LIKE 'joh%' AND email LIKE '%gmail.com';
SELECT symbol_name, symbol_description FROM symbols WHERE LENGTH(symbol_description) > 100 ORDER BY symbol_name;
SELECT trade_id, execution_type, execution_time FROM executions WHERE execution_status = 'completed' ORDER BY execution_time DESC LIMIT 5;
